    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《Pushing》</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是一款仅用鼠标就可以游玩的游戏。游戏以3D式推箱子为主，总共有35个关卡，玩家需要在规定的移动方块次数内将白色方块移动到目的地即可。该游戏并不要求玩家必须在完成一个关卡后才能开启下一个关卡，但推荐玩家按顺序通关。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>操作示例</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鼠标持续按下右键并移动：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/ed35bc42fc5f83af77ae9661cfc8307e.poster.avif?t=1727594259\" width=384 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/ed35bc42fc5f83af77ae9661cfc8307e.webm?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/ed35bc42fc5f83af77ae9661cfc8307e.mp4?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鼠标持续按下右键并移动后左键点击方块：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/842a66ea77ac4bb3f82ac1eec8d9bd44.poster.avif?t=1727594259\" width=384 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/842a66ea77ac4bb3f82ac1eec8d9bd44.webm?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/842a66ea77ac4bb3f82ac1eec8d9bd44.mp4?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>鼠标点击方块不同位置，方块向不同方向移动：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/deedb74812c28225a0bb5c15e79d98f9.poster.avif?t=1727594259\" width=402 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/deedb74812c28225a0bb5c15e79d98f9.webm?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/deedb74812c28225a0bb5c15e79d98f9.mp4?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>推箱子的玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/7bcea08de96ad2c9c954f82de6d2e8a9.poster.avif?t=1727594259\" width=402 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/7bcea08de96ad2c9c954f82de6d2e8a9.webm?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3167480/extras/7bcea08de96ad2c9c954f82de6d2e8a9.mp4?t=1727594259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
